WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
♪To the horizon's call♪

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
♪Put every twist behind you♪

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
♪Drift leisurely through time♪

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
♪Make headway against the wind♪

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
♪Let mountains bow to your pace♪

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
♪Let your nature burst free♪

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.297 --> 01:37.808
=Episode 39=

01:38.256 --> 01:39.215
Move aside! Move!

01:40.415 --> 01:41.376
- Move!
- Get out of the way!

01:41.584 --> 01:42.352
Fire over there!

01:42.352 --> 01:43.088
Fire!

01:43.120 --> 01:43.646
Run!

01:52.376 --> 01:52.976
Let's go.

01:53.896 --> 01:54.656
Okay.

01:54.656 --> 01:55.760
- Fire!
- Fire!

01:55.760 --> 01:56.368
Don't go there!

01:56.368 --> 01:57.736
Hurry up!

01:57.896 --> 01:58.656
Fire!

01:58.656 --> 02:00.376
Escort Ms. Wen and Wuyou home.

02:00.935 --> 02:02.016
- Aren't you coming with us?
- Yes.

02:02.536 --> 02:03.695
I'll go see what's going on.

02:03.896 --> 02:04.816
Don't worry, Ms. Wen.

02:04.816 --> 02:05.896
The guards will protect me.

02:06.616 --> 02:07.855
You must be careful.

02:09.072 --> 02:09.656
Go ahead.

02:14.015 --> 02:15.664
- Fire!
- Fire!

02:23.714 --> 02:25.936
Fire!

02:27.664 --> 02:28.496
Something's off.

02:47.936 --> 02:50.512
- Fire!
- Fire!

02:50.512 --> 02:51.496
- Run!
- Fire!

02:51.575 --> 02:52.536
- Fire!
- Help!

02:52.536 --> 02:53.735
There's a fire! Stay away!

02:53.735 --> 02:54.376
Hurry up!

02:55.015 --> 02:56.415
Fire!

02:58.536 --> 02:59.295
Go!

02:59.455 --> 03:00.216
Come on!

03:02.256 --> 03:02.896
Run!

03:03.615 --> 03:04.376
Qingyu.

03:05.056 --> 03:05.855
Where's Li?

03:06.015 --> 03:06.735
Her Highness

03:06.735 --> 03:08.415
had the guards escort us home.

03:08.496 --> 03:10.216
We don't know where she went either.

03:10.216 --> 03:11.536
But she has guards with her.

03:11.976 --> 03:13.295
Fire!

03:13.936 --> 03:14.695
Yusheng.

03:14.695 --> 03:16.135
Take them to Xiangqi Pavilion.

03:16.240 --> 03:17.104
And I'll go find Li.

03:17.216 --> 03:17.735
Okay.

03:17.735 --> 03:18.256
Got it.

03:18.256 --> 03:19.056
You must be careful.

03:19.135 --> 03:19.855
You all follow me.

03:19.855 --> 03:20.376
Come on!

03:20.735 --> 03:21.256
Go!

03:38.976 --> 03:39.615
Who's there?

04:26.336 --> 04:27.375
You guys

04:28.096 --> 04:30.415
set fires everywhere,
killing innocent people.

04:30.776 --> 04:32.896
Is this how you serve your leader

04:33.096 --> 04:34.495
and achieve your great cause?

04:34.976 --> 04:36.536
This is none of your business.

04:37.536 --> 04:38.495
Either leave

04:40.615 --> 04:42.136
or die.

04:42.656 --> 04:44.415
Let's see who will die.

05:11.336 --> 05:12.096
Are you okay, man?

05:13.776 --> 05:15.175
You're dead!

06:08.615 --> 06:09.696
Run!

06:33.776 --> 06:34.536
Are you okay?

07:35.976 --> 07:36.776
Where are you going?

07:36.776 --> 07:37.615
Mingde Hall.

07:37.815 --> 07:38.615
Stop!

07:39.136 --> 07:40.336
Mo Jingli has led his army

07:40.336 --> 07:41.576
to besiege Mingde Hall.

07:41.935 --> 07:42.976
It's dangerous out there.

07:43.136 --> 07:43.935
You can't go.

07:44.536 --> 07:45.536
I'm the emperor.

07:46.055 --> 07:48.216
Should I cower within the palace walls,

07:48.495 --> 07:50.415
waiting for the rebels
to slaughter my people

07:50.536 --> 07:52.175
until they come kill me?

07:53.696 --> 07:54.495
Stop!

07:54.896 --> 07:55.696
Yanqi.

07:55.935 --> 07:56.896
You can't go.

07:57.536 --> 07:58.815
If anything happens to you,

07:59.216 --> 08:00.696
I won't get through it.

08:02.864 --> 08:03.456
Mother.

08:04.016 --> 08:05.096
I've started to rule.

08:05.456 --> 08:06.415
So, as you said,

08:06.935 --> 08:07.976
I'm able to decide

08:08.375 --> 08:09.216
on my own

08:09.216 --> 08:10.456
whatever happens.

08:24.776 --> 08:25.576
Your Majesty.

08:25.776 --> 08:27.656
Duke Hua has led troops in
to protect you.

08:27.776 --> 08:29.615
He sent me specifically to inform you.

08:29.776 --> 08:31.136
Dachu will certainly be safe.

08:31.735 --> 08:34.296
Dispatch the elite guards
to support them immediately.

08:34.336 --> 08:35.056
Yes.

08:47.696 --> 08:49.072
We traveled day and night,

08:49.176 --> 08:50.855
arriving a day earlier than planned.

08:51.375 --> 08:52.336
But it's still too late.

08:53.072 --> 08:53.696
Listen up.

08:54.255 --> 08:55.216
Set up camp.

08:55.655 --> 08:57.392
We'll enter the palace tomorrow.

08:58.032 --> 08:58.615
Yes.

09:02.176 --> 09:03.216
Run!

09:03.216 --> 09:04.615
Help!

09:05.096 --> 09:05.775
Run!

09:05.775 --> 09:07.015
Go!

09:09.576 --> 09:10.135
Your Highness.

09:11.456 --> 09:12.135
I heard

09:12.135 --> 09:13.696
that to welcome you back,

09:13.696 --> 09:15.792
His Majesty arranged
a three-day lantern event.

09:16.096 --> 09:17.056
Perhaps,

09:17.456 --> 09:18.495
a jubilant crowd

09:18.495 --> 09:19.495
is celebrating.

09:19.495 --> 09:20.895
That's why it sounds noisy.

09:21.264 --> 09:21.895
Your Highness.

09:24.015 --> 09:25.096
We just received a message.

09:25.696 --> 09:26.576
The city is in chaos.

09:27.096 --> 09:28.464
There are fires everywhere.

09:32.775 --> 09:33.576
Send word.

09:33.735 --> 09:35.135
Tell him that I've arrived early.

09:35.135 --> 09:36.216
Have him open the gate.

09:36.216 --> 09:36.735
Yes.

09:44.535 --> 09:47.216
Prince Ding, by imperial decree,
has suppressed the rebellion

09:47.216 --> 09:48.416
and returned in triumph.

09:48.696 --> 09:49.936
We have urgent intelligence

09:49.936 --> 09:52.535
to report to His Majesty immediately.
So, may we enter now?

09:52.535 --> 09:54.296
We've received an imperial order

09:54.296 --> 09:56.216
that Prince Ding is allowed
to enter tomorrow.

09:56.655 --> 09:58.655
Can you quickly report to the palace?

10:00.495 --> 10:01.855
General, please wait a moment.

10:01.936 --> 10:03.816
We will report immediately.

10:04.495 --> 10:05.296
Thank you.

10:07.176 --> 10:07.775
Open the gate!

10:54.375 --> 10:56.015
Guo Jin, an evil woman,

10:56.216 --> 10:57.576
burned down the Eastern Palace

10:57.816 --> 10:58.816
to usurp the throne,

10:58.816 --> 11:00.015
inciting much outrage.

11:00.416 --> 11:02.255
Prince Li is the bloodline
of the late emperor.

11:02.255 --> 11:03.696
Today, by the will of heaven,

11:03.855 --> 11:06.216
we'll execute Guo Jin
and restore order to the nation.

11:06.775 --> 11:09.456
You should now lay down your weapons
and surrender.

11:09.816 --> 11:10.976
What are you waiting for?

11:11.775 --> 11:13.296
Mo Jingli is a rebel

11:13.696 --> 11:14.936
attacking the palace.

11:15.296 --> 11:16.615
That's a capital crime.

11:17.255 --> 11:18.696
All soldiers, hear my command.

11:19.456 --> 11:20.615
Defend the palace.

11:21.096 --> 11:22.216
Kill the rebels.

11:23.184 --> 11:23.952
- Yes!
- Yes!

11:31.615 --> 11:32.696
Loyal souls of Dachu,

11:32.775 --> 11:33.976
fight to the death with me.

11:34.015 --> 11:34.976
What a fool!

11:35.296 --> 11:36.456
Charge!

11:36.775 --> 11:38.216
- Charge!
- Charge!

12:21.535 --> 12:22.296
Suixin!

13:02.535 --> 13:03.336
Your Highness.

13:03.535 --> 13:04.735
Something's wrong in the city.

13:05.936 --> 13:07.015
Have the vanguard

13:07.775 --> 13:08.775
enter the city with me.

13:09.056 --> 13:09.855
What?

13:10.096 --> 13:11.135
You can't, Your Highness.

13:12.056 --> 13:13.416
You now command a large army.

13:13.655 --> 13:15.615
If you enter the city
without an imperial decree,

13:17.015 --> 13:17.895
it means a rebellion.

13:18.895 --> 13:19.696
Your Highness.

13:19.816 --> 13:21.680
The former Prince Ding's death
is a warning.

13:23.296 --> 13:24.096
Your Highness.

13:24.696 --> 13:26.696
The situation in the city
is still unclear.

13:27.336 --> 13:28.775
You must not rush in.

13:35.655 --> 13:36.895
Have an elite unit follow me

13:37.456 --> 13:38.296
into the city.

13:39.296 --> 13:40.015
Yes.

13:40.015 --> 13:40.615
Your Highness.

14:40.416 --> 14:41.488
Escort Duke Hua to safety.

14:41.488 --> 14:42.192
- Yes!
- Yes!

14:42.608 --> 14:43.504
Little Li.

14:43.504 --> 14:44.416
Be careful.

14:53.255 --> 14:54.015
Mo Jingli.

14:55.495 --> 14:57.232
Do you want to be an emperor that much?

14:58.255 --> 14:59.895
So many people died in the city.

15:00.495 --> 15:02.000
The streets ran red with blood.

15:02.416 --> 15:03.135
Tell me.

15:04.096 --> 15:06.056
Since you treat countless lives
as disposable,

15:06.576 --> 15:08.135
do you deserve to rule over the land?

15:09.135 --> 15:10.535
Are you fit to sit on the throne?

15:11.775 --> 15:12.615
Li.

15:13.696 --> 15:14.816
Don't stop me.

15:15.576 --> 15:16.895
What if I do?

15:17.775 --> 15:19.296
Do you want me to die?

15:23.255 --> 15:24.696
I can't turn back now.

15:26.015 --> 15:27.456
At this point,

15:28.655 --> 15:31.135
nothing and no one in this world
can stop me.

15:31.976 --> 15:32.775
You

15:33.056 --> 15:33.855
can't either.

16:48.056 --> 16:48.855
Li.

16:49.375 --> 16:50.255
Get out of the way.

16:51.176 --> 16:52.216
No way.

17:04.696 --> 17:06.376
Then don't blame me for this.

18:13.815 --> 18:14.656
Mo Jingli.

18:15.656 --> 18:16.656
It's all over.

18:17.735 --> 18:18.535
Mo Jingli.

18:19.055 --> 18:20.255
Just surrender.

18:21.015 --> 18:22.095
You killed Yuan Fang

18:22.495 --> 18:23.976
and Princess Lingyun.

18:24.616 --> 18:25.696
You stirred up things.

18:26.176 --> 18:27.295
To usurp the throne,

18:27.976 --> 18:30.055
you even set fires
and slaughtered innocent people.

18:30.856 --> 18:31.896
Such crimes

18:32.656 --> 18:33.575
are unforgivable.

18:43.216 --> 18:44.656
The winner takes all.

18:45.255 --> 18:46.335
Enough talk!

18:48.495 --> 18:49.735
I would rather die

18:50.335 --> 18:51.656
than surrender.

18:54.575 --> 18:55.295
Shoot!

19:27.600 --> 19:30.536
♪Broken halberds and souls
are buried in sand♪

19:31.751 --> 19:33.910
♪Only then did we wake up♪

19:34.964 --> 19:38.661
♪It's destined to lose everything♪

19:39.620 --> 19:42.333
♪It's meant to part♪

19:44.849 --> 19:47.664
♪Moving around throughout life♪

19:48.752 --> 19:51.231
♪Falling in the autumn wind♪

19:51.696 --> 19:55.216
♪Unable to leap into the clouds♪

19:58.335 --> 19:59.735
You haven't changed at all.

20:00.696 --> 20:01.976
Still the same as before.

20:02.856 --> 20:04.456
(You're cowardly and hypocritical.)

20:04.976 --> 20:06.656
You always use noble reasons

20:06.656 --> 20:08.255
to cover up your nasty thoughts.

20:08.255 --> 20:08.976
Over time,

20:09.656 --> 20:10.775
(you start to believe)

20:11.216 --> 20:13.535
(that you're honest and righteous.)

20:14.216 --> 20:14.775
Prince Li.

20:16.216 --> 20:17.535
When you say these words,

20:18.735 --> 20:20.304
don't you find yourself ridiculous?

20:22.096 --> 20:22.736
Li.

20:27.344 --> 20:29.684
♪If I was born in a slump♪

20:29.684 --> 20:32.720
♪How can I remain aloof from the world♪

20:34.672 --> 20:38.459
♪Fighting for one person♪

20:38.936 --> 20:39.656
(Mo Jingli.)

20:40.815 --> 20:42.735
I really despise you.

20:43.815 --> 20:45.335
So stay away from me.

20:45.808 --> 20:49.968
♪It cannot withstand the indifference
of heaven and earth♪

20:52.076 --> 20:54.144
♪The more you care♪

20:54.480 --> 20:59.728
♪The more you feel regret♪

21:18.800 --> 21:24.295
♪Deep love makes one turn hideous♪

21:27.345 --> 21:33.800
♪Having lost, one will stop at nothing
to pursue their own way♪

21:34.704 --> 21:38.681
♪Don't laugh at me
for losing and hurting someone♪

21:39.255 --> 21:41.815
There are seven connected stars.

21:41.815 --> 21:42.535
Count them.

21:43.295 --> 21:44.015
One.

21:44.095 --> 21:44.616
Two.

21:44.616 --> 21:45.335
Look.

21:45.648 --> 21:50.160
♪No need for the victor's pity♪

21:52.775 --> 21:54.015
Did you catch it?

21:54.495 --> 21:55.495
Yes, I did.

21:55.495 --> 21:56.216
Look.

21:56.376 --> 21:57.335
(My life)

21:58.095 --> 21:59.136
(is full of misfortunes.)

22:00.015 --> 22:01.015
(Whatever I wanted,)

22:01.495 --> 22:02.976
(I fought for it myself.)

22:03.376 --> 22:05.584
♪The more you care♪

22:05.735 --> 22:06.456
(Li.)

22:07.295 --> 22:08.815
(Did I do wrong?)

22:39.335 --> 22:40.255
Li.

22:40.696 --> 22:44.255
Why did you place your piece here?

22:45.335 --> 22:46.856
White ones are weak.

22:47.416 --> 22:49.456
If I advance alone again,

22:50.295 --> 22:51.775
I will surely be devoured.

22:54.575 --> 22:55.376
It's better

22:55.416 --> 22:56.696
to work with neighboring pieces

22:57.335 --> 22:58.416
to turn the corner and plan

22:58.735 --> 22:59.656
for what's to come.

23:02.616 --> 23:03.775
Well said.

23:05.775 --> 23:08.295
The chessboard has nineteen lines
across and down,

23:09.815 --> 23:13.575
with 361 intersections.

23:14.176 --> 23:17.936
Each player has 180 pieces.

23:19.015 --> 23:23.656
It's the connection between pieces
that makes the game.

23:31.216 --> 23:32.696
The same goes for everything

23:33.255 --> 23:34.376
in the world.

23:35.295 --> 23:38.255
A tree separated
from the forest will wither.

23:38.896 --> 23:40.272
A single star

23:40.496 --> 23:42.136
will shine lonely.

23:42.936 --> 23:44.775
A person isolated from their connections

23:44.856 --> 23:46.495
will be out of spirits.

23:47.295 --> 23:48.856
Everything in the world

23:48.896 --> 23:50.696
is interdependent.

23:51.376 --> 23:52.416
No one

23:52.575 --> 23:55.896
can live as a solitary piece.

24:05.015 --> 24:05.815
(Li,)

24:06.295 --> 24:07.176
(remember this.)

24:08.495 --> 24:10.896
(Don't let yourself
become a solitary piece.)

24:17.376 --> 24:18.656
Your Highness, are you awake?

24:18.936 --> 24:20.528
If you don't get up, you'll be late.

24:24.976 --> 24:26.176
It's good that you're awake.

24:26.176 --> 24:27.295
You need to wash up quickly.

24:27.295 --> 24:29.095
Ms. Wen is waiting outside.

24:47.656 --> 24:49.255
(Since Mo Jingli's failed coup,)

24:49.735 --> 24:51.176
(more than five months have passed.)

24:51.896 --> 24:53.616
(Inevitably,
inside and outside the court,)

24:53.815 --> 24:55.335
(a major purge took place.)

24:56.735 --> 24:57.648
(But thanks to)

24:57.648 --> 24:59.335
(Gongshu Yang's and Mo Xiuyao's effort,)

24:59.656 --> 25:01.656
(the court did not
experience major upheaval.)

25:02.176 --> 25:02.976
(The capital)

25:03.136 --> 25:05.136
(soon returned to peace.)

25:08.456 --> 25:09.616
(Last New Year's Eve,)

25:10.255 --> 25:11.495
(the Empress Dowager fell ill.)

25:12.055 --> 25:13.055
(When I saw her again,)

25:13.456 --> 25:14.575
(she had aged a lot.)

25:16.495 --> 25:17.696
(She saw me)

25:17.896 --> 25:19.176
(but remained silent.)

25:20.095 --> 25:21.936
(She just sat quietly
outside Anqing Palace,)

25:23.295 --> 25:25.255
(watching the setting sun
in the distance.)

25:28.616 --> 25:29.376
Princess Ding.

25:38.295 --> 25:39.696
(Duke Hua told me)

25:40.095 --> 25:42.735
(that His Majesty already knows
what the Empress Dowager did.)

25:42.735 --> 25:44.896
(But so far, no decree regarding her
has been issued.)

25:45.495 --> 25:47.575
(It's indeed hard for His Majesty)

25:47.856 --> 25:49.136
(to choose)

25:49.535 --> 25:50.696
(between mother and justice.)

25:51.176 --> 25:52.696
(So I told Duke Hua)

25:53.255 --> 25:54.456
(we could wait)

25:54.936 --> 25:56.856
(and give His Majesty more time.)

26:02.856 --> 26:05.295
(Mo Xiuyao went to Suixue Pass again.)

26:05.856 --> 26:07.136
(He had to lead troops)

26:07.775 --> 26:09.815
(to deal with the remnants
of the rebels.)

26:10.656 --> 26:11.735
(And I...)

26:15.095 --> 26:15.896
Your Highness.

26:16.095 --> 26:18.055
I remember
you had three straw figures before.

26:18.055 --> 26:19.376
Did you throw them all away?

26:23.055 --> 26:25.255
Can I not wear many hair accessories?

26:26.055 --> 26:27.775
Do you have a headache again?

26:29.055 --> 26:30.095
Too many hair accessories

26:30.176 --> 26:31.015
are heavy.

26:31.335 --> 26:32.735
Today, you have to go with Ms. Wen

26:32.735 --> 26:34.416
to the Jinchang Shop
to try on new clothes.

26:34.416 --> 26:36.815
You need to be properly dressed
to go with the new clothes.

26:36.815 --> 26:37.495
By the way,

26:37.495 --> 26:39.015
Ms. Wen specifically instructed us

26:39.055 --> 26:41.055
to do your hair well

26:41.416 --> 26:42.656
to make you more elegant,

26:42.896 --> 26:43.936
noble,

26:44.136 --> 26:45.376
and stunning,

26:46.456 --> 26:47.255
Li.

26:48.495 --> 26:50.335
Li, hurry up. We're going to be late.

26:50.335 --> 26:51.216
Almost done.

26:52.456 --> 26:54.976
If I hadn't ordered top-quality fabric
at Jinchang Shop,

26:54.976 --> 26:57.216
I wouldn't have rushed you
to get up today.

26:57.575 --> 26:58.936
This fabric is very expensive.

26:58.976 --> 27:01.015
Many ladies in the capital
couldn't get on the list.

27:01.015 --> 27:01.656
I think

27:01.656 --> 27:03.376
you should go try it on yourself.

27:07.015 --> 27:09.216
(Lately, Ms. Wen has made new friends.)

27:09.616 --> 27:11.815
(She often drinks tea, enjoys flowers,)

27:12.015 --> 27:13.176
(and chats with them.)

27:14.216 --> 27:16.015
(Probably,
she's afraid I'll feel lonely)

27:16.095 --> 27:17.295
(when Mo Xiuyao is not home.)

27:17.775 --> 27:18.936
(Wherever she goes,)

27:19.015 --> 27:20.856
(she always wants to take me along.)

27:21.856 --> 27:23.255
(But actually, I don't want to go.)

27:23.936 --> 27:25.216
(Because my head hurts.)

27:27.495 --> 27:29.255
Lady Zhao will host a banquet soon.

27:29.295 --> 27:31.015
I will buy her a gift then.

27:31.015 --> 27:32.815
I decided to buy a dress for her.

27:32.815 --> 27:34.295
So I invited her to come along.

27:34.735 --> 27:35.495
Later,

27:35.495 --> 27:38.055
after we finish trying on clothes,
let's go have some tea.

27:40.936 --> 27:41.535
Li.

27:42.416 --> 27:44.495
Did you hear what I just said?

27:44.815 --> 27:45.416
I'm listening.

27:47.495 --> 27:49.535
It's been almost five months
since Yao left.

27:49.976 --> 27:50.936
In the past five months,

27:51.055 --> 27:52.295
unless I take you out,

27:52.535 --> 27:54.095
you've never left the house,

27:54.095 --> 27:55.696
shutting yourself in your room.

27:55.696 --> 27:56.856
At such a young age,

27:56.856 --> 27:58.696
how can you endure loneliness?

28:01.648 --> 28:02.896
These days,

28:02.896 --> 28:04.896
you eat and sleep
and then sleep and eat again.

28:05.095 --> 28:06.896
You're supposed to be gaining weight.

28:07.216 --> 28:08.896
But why does your face

28:08.976 --> 28:10.216
look even thinner?

28:12.295 --> 28:12.856
Let's go.

28:20.815 --> 28:21.616
Ms. Wen.

28:22.216 --> 28:23.936
After I take you to the shop,

28:24.055 --> 28:25.376
can I come back and wait for you?

28:25.896 --> 28:27.775
I don't need to try on my dress.

28:27.775 --> 28:29.136
That won't do.

28:29.176 --> 28:31.176
You have to try on the dress

28:31.176 --> 28:32.376
to make alterations.

28:32.376 --> 28:33.815
It will look perfect on you then.

28:49.535 --> 28:50.456
Madam, welcome.

28:52.696 --> 28:53.976
This must be Princess Ding.

28:54.936 --> 28:56.936
She is stunning,
perfect for the Yunjin brocade.

28:57.575 --> 28:58.416
Thanks.

28:58.535 --> 28:59.535
Has Lady Zhao arrived?

28:59.535 --> 29:01.055
Yes, she's been here for a while.

29:01.255 --> 29:02.176
Ms. Wen.

29:02.696 --> 29:03.495
Your Highness.

29:03.616 --> 29:05.616
Today, the shop has new fabric.

29:05.616 --> 29:07.015
- Let's go take a look.
- Really?

29:07.015 --> 29:07.976
Li, come on.

29:08.735 --> 29:09.656
When did you arrive?

29:09.656 --> 29:11.015
Have you been waiting long?

29:11.015 --> 29:11.735
Not long.

29:11.735 --> 29:12.856
I just arrived as well.

29:15.015 --> 29:15.575
Look.

29:22.095 --> 29:23.015
Nice fabric.

29:23.335 --> 29:24.095
Don't get it dirty.

29:25.495 --> 29:26.575
If you place a piece there,

29:27.095 --> 29:28.376
it will become a solitary piece.

29:29.255 --> 29:31.616
But that is
what the chess manual teaches.

29:31.976 --> 29:32.535
Look.

29:52.456 --> 29:53.255
Li.

29:54.095 --> 29:55.495
- Xing, look.
- Li.

29:55.575 --> 29:56.216
Come on.

29:56.216 --> 29:57.376
Go try on clothes.

29:58.616 --> 30:00.055
Why are you looking at it?

30:00.616 --> 30:01.656
This fabric.

30:01.656 --> 30:02.575
I like it.

30:02.976 --> 30:04.896
If Your Highness likes it, just take it.

30:06.856 --> 30:07.456
Well,

30:07.456 --> 30:08.456
try on the clothes first,

30:08.456 --> 30:09.656
and come back to get it later.

30:09.896 --> 30:10.495
Come on.

30:14.480 --> 30:15.815
(Qingfeng Mingyue Tower)

30:15.815 --> 30:16.976
Her Highness is here.

30:17.040 --> 30:18.216
- You must sit here.
- Come.

30:18.216 --> 30:19.616
Sit down.

30:19.616 --> 30:20.616
I want you to meet them.

30:20.616 --> 30:23.255
This is Lady Gao, Lady Liu,
Lady Wang, and Lady Zhao.

30:23.255 --> 30:23.976
Come on.

30:23.976 --> 30:25.136
Why are you late?

30:25.136 --> 30:26.136
We've been waiting.

30:26.136 --> 30:26.696
Lady Zhao.

30:26.696 --> 30:27.376
You've met.

30:27.376 --> 30:27.976
Hurry up.

30:27.976 --> 30:29.055
- Yes.
- Come on.

30:31.055 --> 30:31.815
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

30:31.815 --> 30:33.055
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

30:34.456 --> 30:35.376
It smells so good.

30:36.696 --> 30:37.656
Have some more.

30:38.936 --> 30:41.095
Look, this hair accessory is so pretty.

31:11.015 --> 31:12.376
Li, it's time to eat.

31:13.055 --> 31:14.696
- It's time to eat, Li.
- Sure.

31:28.815 --> 31:29.575
Your Highness.

31:30.335 --> 31:31.815
Your Highness, the tea is ready.

31:50.015 --> 31:51.015
Steward Cui.

31:51.735 --> 31:54.136
Prepare a light breakfast
for Her Highness tomorrow.

31:54.575 --> 31:55.176
Alright.

31:55.176 --> 31:56.015
I'll arrange it.

32:04.295 --> 32:05.535
It's not finished.

32:05.656 --> 32:06.976
Go store it away.

32:06.976 --> 32:07.775
Yes.

32:25.055 --> 32:25.856
Li.

32:27.896 --> 32:28.535
Ms. Wen.

32:32.055 --> 32:33.495
What's wrong with you?

32:34.255 --> 32:35.815
You've been absent-minded.

32:40.456 --> 32:41.295
Why do you

32:41.335 --> 32:43.255
often watch this pot of flowers?

32:46.976 --> 32:48.136
I like it.

32:52.416 --> 32:54.015
Yao will be back soon.

32:54.575 --> 32:56.216
These past months have been hard on you.

32:57.015 --> 32:58.735
If he hadn't gone to Suixue Pass,

32:59.176 --> 33:00.896
we could have brought him back.

33:03.535 --> 33:04.696
Bring him back?

33:04.936 --> 33:05.735
Yes.

33:06.575 --> 33:09.495
But Suixue Pass is quite far.

33:22.960 --> 33:29.552
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

33:32.976 --> 33:39.280
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

33:41.488 --> 33:44.720
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

33:44.944 --> 33:50.960
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

33:51.504 --> 33:59.656
♪To the horizon's call,
your journey hasn't started♪

33:59.656 --> 34:00.856
(I will go welcome him back)
I will go bring him back.

34:02.581 --> 34:06.352
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

34:06.352 --> 34:12.080
♪The world is renewed♪

34:12.749 --> 34:16.624
♪The resilience grown from regrets♪

34:16.624 --> 34:21.200
♪All are gifts♪

34:21.736 --> 34:22.976
(I want to see Mo Xiuyao.)

34:24.055 --> 34:25.456
(The thread broke at some point.)

34:26.495 --> 34:28.015
(I drift in time.)

34:28.495 --> 34:29.655
(I awake,)

34:30.095 --> 34:31.336
(or I dream.)

34:32.256 --> 34:33.376
(I'm at a loss,)

34:33.736 --> 34:34.856
(feeling dizzy,)

34:35.495 --> 34:36.936
(like a stranded stone,)

34:37.336 --> 34:39.015
(like a solitary piece on a chessboard.)

34:40.376 --> 34:41.495
(But just now,)

34:42.175 --> 34:43.615
(my mind)

34:43.615 --> 34:44.816
(was struck by a thought:)

34:45.736 --> 34:46.896
(go find him.)

34:47.816 --> 34:49.015
(Go now.)

34:58.135 --> 34:59.535
(Like when I was little,)

34:59.896 --> 35:01.296
(just leave without hesitation.)

35:05.095 --> 35:06.015
(But that time,)

35:06.936 --> 35:08.175
(I couldn't find him.)

35:13.488 --> 35:18.640
♪The unknown journey♪

35:18.714 --> 35:23.727
♪No need to ask♪

35:23.727 --> 35:27.088
♪All that you wait for and seek♪

35:27.088 --> 35:34.192
♪Will come true♪

35:37.655 --> 35:38.704
(What about this time?)

35:39.695 --> 35:40.856
(I don't know.)

35:42.856 --> 35:44.720
(But I still want
to ride the fastest horse,)

35:45.135 --> 35:46.175
(ride the wind,)

35:47.175 --> 35:48.336
(and cross the mountains)

35:48.976 --> 35:51.336
(and the chessboard-like world.)

35:51.615 --> 35:52.655
(Faster,)

35:52.655 --> 35:53.456
(and faster.)

35:54.215 --> 35:56.615
(I'll get so fast that a long thread
trails behind me,)

35:57.175 --> 35:59.760
(reconnecting me to this world.)

35:59.760 --> 36:05.264
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

36:05.648 --> 36:09.439
♪Let your nature burst free♪

36:09.887 --> 36:11.776
♪Unbound by form♪

36:11.776 --> 36:12.816
Once it's all over here,

36:13.135 --> 36:15.575
Jin and I will head back to the capital.

36:16.816 --> 36:18.736
We won't accompany you back to camp.

36:19.175 --> 36:20.095
Yes, Your Highness.

36:23.135 --> 36:23.936
In the future,

36:24.655 --> 36:26.064
Suixue Pass is entrusted to you.

36:26.896 --> 36:27.896
You'll deter Cangbei

36:28.336 --> 36:29.376
and defend the frontier.

36:30.055 --> 36:30.976
That's a serious job.

36:31.456 --> 36:32.456
You must be wary.

36:34.175 --> 36:35.175
Yes, Your Highness.

36:35.655 --> 36:37.896
I will do my utmost

36:38.055 --> 36:39.256
to guard the pass

36:39.615 --> 36:40.896
and not fail your trust.

36:46.615 --> 36:47.416
Has there been

36:47.736 --> 36:49.095
no letter from home?

36:51.015 --> 36:52.095
No.

36:57.095 --> 36:59.535
No wonder Your Highness
is so eager to return.

37:00.095 --> 37:02.448
Turns out you haven't received a letter
from Her Highness.

37:05.376 --> 37:06.175
Mo Xiuyao!

37:10.936 --> 37:11.736
Mo Xiuyao!

37:12.936 --> 37:13.535
That's...

37:14.215 --> 37:14.936
Her Highness.

37:21.584 --> 37:22.363
Whoa!

37:28.776 --> 37:29.495
Why are you here?

37:37.976 --> 37:38.615
It's a long way.

37:38.976 --> 37:40.055
You shouldn't have come.

37:41.416 --> 37:42.936
But I want to come and bring you back.

37:46.655 --> 37:47.504
Give me your hand.

37:54.256 --> 37:55.896
Maybe I should do it myself.

37:58.936 --> 37:59.535
The other one.

38:03.015 --> 38:03.936
Is that

38:03.936 --> 38:05.135
Suixue Pass out there?

38:07.296 --> 38:08.575
Didn't you come here as a child?

38:09.256 --> 38:10.615
I was too young then

38:10.615 --> 38:11.535
to remember the way.

38:13.296 --> 38:14.175
You don't remember,

38:14.936 --> 38:16.655
but you still came here alone.

38:22.376 --> 38:23.655
This is Guima Fort.

38:24.615 --> 38:26.615
It's still over 100 li to Suixue Pass.

38:27.856 --> 38:28.776
If you didn't

38:29.135 --> 38:30.856
run into me here,

38:31.175 --> 38:31.976
you would sleep

38:32.296 --> 38:33.816
in the wilderness tonight.

38:34.456 --> 38:36.256
At night, the wolves howl everywhere,

38:36.816 --> 38:37.615
and perhaps,

38:37.816 --> 38:39.055
there are also horse bandits.

38:43.135 --> 38:44.495
Then I'm really lucky.

38:52.336 --> 38:53.615
But I missed you.

38:54.856 --> 38:56.416
Right after the capital turmoil ended,

38:56.695 --> 38:57.615
you left.

38:58.215 --> 38:59.856
We haven't seen each other for so long.

39:01.215 --> 39:02.896
Didn't I write to you?

39:04.336 --> 39:05.360
That's not the same.

39:07.615 --> 39:08.495
In the capital,

39:09.055 --> 39:09.896
I wasn't happy.

39:10.936 --> 39:13.495
Qingyu overdid my hair every day,

39:13.976 --> 39:15.456
hurting my head.

39:16.495 --> 39:17.896
Ms. Wen was afraid I'd be lonely,

39:18.175 --> 39:20.095
so she often took me
to various banquets.

39:20.495 --> 39:22.135
Those ladies

39:22.135 --> 39:24.256
love to talk about clothes,
jewelry, and gossip.

39:24.816 --> 39:25.936
I couldn't fit in.

39:29.695 --> 39:31.175
You can take care of your shop.

39:32.416 --> 39:33.495
Han Mingxi left.

39:33.655 --> 39:35.776
The new staff aren't familiar with me.

39:36.495 --> 39:38.015
Tang Zixiao is quite capable,

39:38.256 --> 39:40.175
even more capable than Wei Zhuang.

39:40.816 --> 39:41.816
Even if I'm there,

39:41.936 --> 39:43.215
I can't help at all.

39:44.456 --> 39:45.655
Indeed, you shouldn't go then.

39:46.495 --> 39:48.256
Mr. Li isn't in the capital either.

39:48.655 --> 39:50.896
He's traveling with Lady Yusheng,

39:50.896 --> 39:52.055
living a carefree life.

39:52.535 --> 39:54.015
I haven't seen him for a long time.

39:54.736 --> 39:55.936
So, you came to find me?

40:02.192 --> 40:02.695
Sure.

40:03.896 --> 40:04.856
With you,

40:05.015 --> 40:05.936
I can walk on the line

40:06.575 --> 40:08.015
and not become a solitary piece.

40:08.495 --> 40:10.215
What line? Solitary piece?

40:10.896 --> 40:12.135
What are you talking about?

40:15.856 --> 40:16.856
I just missed you.

40:18.615 --> 40:20.615
Even so, you can't do this.

40:21.215 --> 40:23.256
Traveling all the way alone
is dangerous.

40:23.776 --> 40:25.776
What if you run into bandits

40:26.456 --> 40:27.535
on the way?

40:29.135 --> 40:30.416
They can't beat me.

40:35.376 --> 40:36.135
Got it.

40:37.256 --> 40:38.215
You must promise.

40:38.456 --> 40:39.655
Don't just pretend to agree,

40:40.256 --> 40:42.135
and then forget my words
the next moment.

40:44.135 --> 40:45.095
I promise.

40:46.615 --> 40:47.736
I know you're not serious.

40:51.816 --> 40:52.856
- Guys.
- Come on!

40:52.856 --> 40:54.416
We rarely feel so happy today.

40:54.456 --> 40:55.736
Let's have a toast, shall we?

40:55.736 --> 40:56.376
Come on!

40:56.376 --> 40:57.336
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

40:57.336 --> 40:58.256
Everyone, join in.

40:58.256 --> 40:59.135
Bottoms up!

41:00.976 --> 41:01.736
Your Highness.

41:01.736 --> 41:03.816
Try this. I got it specially for you.

41:03.816 --> 41:05.376
- It's delicious.
- Thanks, General Wang.

41:05.856 --> 41:06.495
Delicious.

41:09.336 --> 41:10.175
Smells so good.

41:10.575 --> 41:12.575
I've heard a lot about you
from His Highness.

41:12.896 --> 41:15.135
Today, you came here alone

41:15.175 --> 41:16.055
from so far away.

41:16.336 --> 41:18.615
I admire you very much.

41:19.095 --> 41:20.416
And I'm also somewhat moved.

41:23.215 --> 41:24.256
We rarely gather together.

41:25.135 --> 41:27.215
So, this is to both of you.

41:27.776 --> 41:28.896
I wish you both

41:29.535 --> 41:30.535
grow old together

41:30.655 --> 41:31.456
and never part.

41:31.776 --> 41:32.936
I'll drink it up.

41:32.936 --> 41:33.896
To both of you.

41:35.135 --> 41:36.055
Your Highnesses.

41:36.695 --> 41:37.695
I'm drinking water.

41:38.575 --> 41:39.215
What?

41:39.615 --> 41:40.336
Drinking water?

41:41.976 --> 41:42.776
With her.

41:44.055 --> 41:45.055
Drinking water with me?

41:45.695 --> 41:47.015
Can't I drink liquor either?

41:47.336 --> 41:49.336
You've been riding for days.
You must be tired.

41:49.416 --> 41:50.256
You need to rest.

41:51.816 --> 41:52.656
So I came all the way

41:52.936 --> 41:54.376
for nothing, not even a drink.

41:54.655 --> 41:55.256
Cheers.

41:58.776 --> 42:00.095
How about a dance?

42:00.095 --> 42:01.256
Okay, come on!

42:02.456 --> 42:03.175
Come on!

42:03.695 --> 42:04.495
General Wang.

42:05.495 --> 42:06.936
Do you want to dance too?

42:11.376 --> 42:12.816
Let's dance.

42:13.456 --> 42:14.095
Go.

42:14.095 --> 42:15.256
- Dance.
- Dance.

42:30.055 --> 42:30.856
- Awesome.
- Awesome.

42:31.095 --> 42:31.896
Awesome.

42:35.695 --> 42:36.256
Impressive.

42:41.509 --> 42:44.240
(Preview)

42:44.336 --> 42:45.535
I'm going on a long journey,

42:45.936 --> 42:46.655
traveling around

42:47.055 --> 42:48.135
and living a carefree life.

42:48.135 --> 42:49.376
Before I left the mountain,

42:49.456 --> 42:51.336
I had four people in mind
I wanted to eliminate.

42:51.535 --> 42:52.776
What number am I?

42:53.015 --> 42:53.695
Number four.

42:53.776 --> 42:54.655
Now

42:55.135 --> 42:56.456
is a good opportunity for you.

42:56.655 --> 42:58.015
(Lishan Academy)
If poor scholars come

42:58.015 --> 42:59.575
to Lishan Academy for education,

42:59.575 --> 43:00.856
we'll provide them

43:01.256 --> 43:03.175
with full tuition in Li's name.

43:03.175 --> 43:05.776
A good cook doesn't mean a good teacher.

43:05.776 --> 43:06.615
What do you mean?

43:07.015 --> 43:07.896
Let's have a contest.

43:15.736 --> 43:22.328
♪Memories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreams♪

43:25.912 --> 43:32.056
♪Only by moving forward
can you find reunion♪

43:34.264 --> 43:37.496
♪Endings only mark new routes♪

43:37.720 --> 43:43.736
♪It's all part of the scenery♪

43:44.056 --> 43:47.480
♪To the horizon's call♪

43:47.544 --> 43:54.104
♪Your journey hasn't started♪

43:55.160 --> 43:59.096
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

43:59.096 --> 44:04.792
♪Both joy and grief
make the trip worthwhile♪

44:05.304 --> 44:13.912
♪Trying to catch up
to your own lost shadow♪

44:14.808 --> 44:20.312
♪Within the wilds, echoes thrive♪

44:20.312 --> 44:25.816
♪Clear mind leads to a clear path♪

44:25.880 --> 44:29.944
♪Be grateful to your losses♪

44:30.232 --> 44:35.456
♪Make your steps weightless♪

44:36.056 --> 44:39.768
♪Towards mountains,
chase the stars bright♪

44:39.800 --> 44:45.464
♪Let time embrace you
and wash away the past♪

44:46.232 --> 44:54.200
♪Put every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through time♪

44:55.608 --> 45:00.856
♪Make headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your pace♪

45:01.112 --> 45:07.016
♪Rush towards a life without regret♪

45:07.016 --> 45:11.136
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:11.352 --> 45:16.088
♪Unbound by form♪

45:17.304 --> 45:21.576
♪Let your nature burst free♪

45:21.816 --> 45:27.256
♪Unbound by form♪
